---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContentFooter from '../components/ContentFooter.astro';
import ContentHeader from '../components/ContentHeader.astro';
---
<Layout>
  <syn-card>
    <ContentHeader headline="Out of scope and non-goals" headlineClass="syn-heading--2x-large" />

    <p>
      This page describes areas that are intentionally
      <strong>out of scope</strong> for the Synergy Design System.
      It clarifies system boundaries to prevent incorrect assumptions.
      This page is non-normative and does not define component behavior or API contracts.
    </p>

    <h2 class="syn-heading--large">Explicit non-goals</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Synergy does not define application-specific business logic.</li>
      <li>Synergy does not define backend APIs or server-side data validation.</li>
      <li>Synergy does not define product-specific UX flows or user journeys.</li>
      <li>Synergy does not define content strategy, tone of voice, or copywriting.</li>
      <li>Synergy does not define non-web (native mobile or desktop) UI frameworks.</li>
    </ul>

    <ContentFooter
      creationDate={new Date().toISOString()}
      entityId={null}
    >
      | Normative component behavior and API contracts are defined on individual component pages.
    </ContentFooter>

  </syn-card>
</Layout>
